{"tid":2410177,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台擬修憲 投票權調低至18歲","createTime":"2021-02-16T11:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T12:19:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e26653100884a588c83d43768c52342373a549","tid":2410177,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/35GT4SJB55FVHHYNY4JKP3FJWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2F35GT4SJB55FVHHYNY4JKP3FJWA%2F&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BW8HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=66ac8bde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2F35GT4SJB55FVHHYNY4JKP3FJWA%2F&h=1eb09087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/35GT4SJB55FVHHYNY4JKP3FJWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n台擬修憲 投票權調低至18歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J-zESUQTvflU0z1eY2c_3EUlxvc=/1577x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MD7FCP6Y3FDTFNVTQ6SCNP5SYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ-zESUQTvflU0z1eY2c_3EUlxvc%3D%2F1577x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMD7FCP6Y3FDTFNVTQ6SCNP5SYU.jpg&h=f44041d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣立法院年後將啟動修憲議程。<br />\n<br />\n台灣立法院新會期即將開始，立法院長游錫堃日前預告將啟動修憲委員會，目前收到43個《憲法》與《憲法增修條文》修正草案。朝野立委普遍認同將目前20歲才擁有的選舉權，下調至18歲。不過修憲亦須公民投票，估計要965萬票才可生效，並不容易。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n須獲965萬票門檻高<br />\n<br />\n修憲過往在台灣視為「不可能任務」，憲法修正案要立法院院1/4立委（29人）提議、超過3/4（85人）人出席，並一致支持提出修憲草案。半年後修正案要經台灣一半選民，即965萬人以上投票同意，才會真正通過生效。目前最有可能獲立委通過的是「18歲公民權」，目前獲台灣各政黨支持，將20歲才有投票權，下調至18歲，但分歧在於被選舉權的年齡。目前台灣是23歲才有被選舉權，立委們分別主張維持23歲、下調至20歲、下調至18歲三個方案。 有綠營立委提出修改《憲法增修條文》中有關「國家統一」、「固有疆域」的規定，因涉及主權，國民黨提議退回程序委員會。<br />\n<br />\n此外，民眾黨、時代力量亦表示願意支持降低修憲門檻。無黨籍立委林昶佐提案降低門檻為「立委2/3出席」；公民複決門檻由「有效同意票超過選舉人總額之半數」降低成「有效票超過選舉總額半數，同意票多於不同意票」。比對蔡英文2020年總統大選，獲得817萬史上最高選票，距離修憲過半門檻965萬票仍有差距，相信法案通過仍然有難度。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"281932b7ffd23745e72170c5b4bdf79dfdf5afce","tid":2410177,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>順便特赦陳同佳</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1e02503e214c62586117d36c878e3aa0b8dbce","tid":2410177,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"死廢老KMT慢慢絕種<br />\n民進黨不停有新血加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5362125a1493016568ed0ba60d850c9cd83104","tid":2410177,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"原來宜家台灣要23歲先有投票權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e025e2d9e6aef23c1b2616dca3f9c64a0ef7814","tid":2410177,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b5362125a1493016568ed0ba60d850c9cd83104","tid":2410177,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"原來宜家台灣要23歲先有投票權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"將目前20歲才擁有的選舉權，下調至18歲"},{"pid":"7bd64d451fecf032de081f3b48ae8ba44b922dea","tid":2410177,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b5362125a1493016568ed0ba60d850c9cd83104","tid":2410177,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"原來宜家台灣要23歲先有投票權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"投票權：20歲下調至18歲<br />\n被選舉權：23歲，分別主張維持23歲、下調至20歲、下調至18歲三個方案"},{"pid":"81d3dbfe8a2aaef484a0bb717c319e8b129b5b3c","tid":2410177,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e025e2d9e6aef23c1b2616dca3f9c64a0ef7814","tid":2410177,"uid":25558,"like":1